    Lab 2: Reading from a File
    The WordCounterApp class provides a main method for a program that counts the words in a line. This program reads lines from the book "Alice in Wonderland" and prints some of those lines. It calculates the number of lines read and prints that number before each printed line. It also calculates the average line length for the text that is printed as well as the entire book.
